sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as User Interface
    participant E as Code Editor
    participant M as Mermaid Core
    participant P as Preview Panel
    participant S as Storage Service
    participant AI as AI Service
    participant LLM as LLM Provider

    Note over U,LLM: Diagram Creation Flow

    U->>UI: Click "New Diagram"
    UI->>S: Create empty diagram
    S->>UI: Return diagram ID
    UI->>E: Open new tab with empty content

    U->>E: Start typing diagram code
    E->>E: Debounce input (300ms)
    E->>M: renderDiagram(content, id)
    M->>M: Parse & validate syntax
    M->>M: Render SVG with theme
    M->>P: Update preview
    P->>UI: Display rendered diagram

    U->>E: Press Ctrl+S to save
    E->>S: saveDiagram(diagram)
    S->>S: Store in localStorage
    S->>E: Update tab as saved
    E->>UI: Show "Saved" notification

    Note over U,LLM: AI Generation Flow

    U->>UI: Click "AI Generate" button
    UI->>AI: Open AI panel
    AI->>UI: Show prompt input
    U->>AI: "Create a flowchart for user registration"
    AI->>LLM: API call with prompt
    LLM->>AI: Return generated diagram
    AI->>E: Insert generated code
    E->>M: renderDiagram(content, id)
    M->>P: Update preview

    Note over U,LLM: Error Handling Flow

    M->>M: Detect syntax error
    M->>E: Display error message
    E->>UI: Show error in status bar
    U->>UI: Click "Fix with AI"
    UI->>AI: Call fixDiagram with error
    AI->>LLM: API call with error context
    LLM->>AI: Return fixed code
    AI->>E: Replace with fixed code

    Note over U,LLM: Version Control Flow

    U->>UI: Click "Show History"
    UI->>S: Get version history
    S->>UI: Return version list
    UI->>UI: Show history modal
    U->>UI: Select version to restore
    UI->>E: Replace content with selected version
    E->>M: renderDiagram(content, id)
    M->>P: Update preview